name: Fire of life (Henwee)
description:
Ludum dare 46 submission

"Keep it alive"

Keep the water from touching "The fire of life". If the fire goes out, you will die. Also, don't touch the fire, since you are made of leaves. The fire contains the energy that keeps you alive.

Try to beat my high score of 1235 points, i have no doubt that you can do it
